1. Enterprise Knowledge Assistant

Can be used as an internal AI assistant for organizations to answer employee queries based on company documents, SOPs, policies, and manuals.

2. Customer Support Automation

The agent can handle customer queries by retrieving information from product documentation, FAQs, and knowledge bases, reducing dependency on human support teams.

3. HR Policy & Onboarding Assistant

Helps employees understand HR policies, leave rules, benefits, and onboarding material by querying internal HR documents.

4. Research & Learning Assistant

Supports students, researchers, and analysts by retrieving relevant content from PDFs, notes, or research documents and generating summarized, accurate answers.

5. Legal & Compliance Document Assistant

Can be adapted to search through contracts, compliance guidelines, and policy documents to answer regulation-related queries with reduced hallucination.

6. Education & Training Platforms

Useful for e-learning platforms where learners can ask questions from course material and receive context-aware explanations.
